com.wingman.client.api.plugin

Annotation Type Plugin.Refresh


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
@Target(value=METHOD)
public static @interface Plugin.Refresh
    Use this interface to annotate the refresh method.
    The refresh method should initialize and cleanup all things that require cross-plugin interaction.
    This method should be the only place where you negotiate with other plugins.
    This method will be called every time other plugins are loaded or unloaded.
    This method must be static.
